Title: American Made Grills Estate 30-Inch Freestanding Grill - Natural Gas - ESTFS30-NG
Description: American Made Grills Estate 30" Freestanding Natural Gas Grill The Estate Grill series includes full-featured luxury gas grills built in the USA. Crafted with precision to meet your highest grilling standards, loaded with the features you expect from a grill in the Luxury class. 3 Red Brass Burners, Plus an Infrared Back Burner The Estate natural gas grill employs durable red brass burners, combined with ceramic briquette flame tamers to provide consistent heat (and, obviously, to reduce flare-ups). The 3 burners deliver 78,000 BTUs beneath a total grilling area over 1,000 square inches. You don't often see red brass used in grill burners, primarily because it's more expensive than stainless steel. And, let's face it, it looks cooler! In addition, you'll enjoy the back infrared burner, which puts out 20,000 BTUs to roast meats on the (included) rotisserie. Stainless Steel Construction Constructed with 304 stainless steel including heavy-duty 9 mm cooking grates, 18-gauge double-lined hood with spring assist and a full-width hood handle. the AMG Estate grill is built to last and give you years of reliable service. Blue Knob Lighting You should never have to guess at what levels your burners are set, especially after dark. The American Made Grill Estate series includes blue illumination above each knob to help you see what you're doing no matter the time of day. Interior Halogen Lighting Speaking of grilling at night, is there anything worse than opening the hood and not really seeing what's going on in there? With the Estate series, when you open the hood halogen lights illuminate your cooking surface. Never squint again or be tempted to get a closer look at the meat (and get an accidental "suntan" on your face) to see if it's ready to flip, or how close it is to done. Stainless Steel Grill Cart with Storage Talk about grilling convenience! The Estate 30" Grill Cart features double access doors with storage space, ventilation, and locking caster wheels. It arrives fully assembled . Rotisserie Spit Storage Keep your rotisserie spit close by with integrated storage built into the grill. Rotisserie kit is included. Made in the USA? You bet! It's in the name: American Made Grills are built, tested, and serviced in the USA. Included Accessories - a $1,000+ Value! Each American Made Grill 30" Estate gas grill comes with: Rotisserie Kit Heavy Duty PVC Grill Cover Stainless Steel Griddle 26,000 BTU Drop-in Infrared Sear Burner Smoker Tray Care Kit American Made Grills 30" Estate FAQ Can I convert the AMG Estate 30-in natural gas grill to propane? There isn't a gas conversion kit available for AMG grills, but they make a propane version with the same price, specs and features, the ESTFS30-NG . Title: American Made Grills 6.6c Deluxe Outdoor Rated Kegerator - No Tap - AMG-RFR-24DK
Description: Bring the party to your outdoor space with this American Made Grills kegerator body. This kegerator is fully constructed in 304 grade stainless steel and features front venting allowing the kegerator to be used built-in to your outdoor kitchen or freestanding. This unit pairs with our single or double taps (AMG-RFR-TAP-1, AMG-RFR-TAP-2), or a compatible tap of your choosing. The 6.6 cubic feet of cold storage provides ample space for multiple slim kegs to be served. The front mounted digital thermostat allows you to adjust the internal temperature so that your beer is always perfectly cooled. The durable construction, sealed back, and UL rating makes this unit ideal for use outdoors. The kegerator has a wrap-around 304 grade stainless steel body and door with a full-length, professional handle for a sleek and stylish finish. Adjustable leveling legs are included to ensure your kegerator sits evenly on any patio surface while a door lock provides security. This AMG-RFR-24Dk model is UL Certified for Outdoor Use. Title: American Made Grills Estate 42-Inch Grill Liner - GL-EST42
Description: Protect your outdoor kitchen with American Made Grills Grill Insulating Jackets. Many BBQ Islands and outdoor kitchens are made of a combination of wood and other combustible materials. A grill insulating jacket provides the protection you need to ensure a safe and reliable entertaining space for years to come. Custom made to fit American Made Grills Grills, each grill insulating jacket features durable double-lined 304 stainless steel construction for maximum strength and protection, stainless steel mounting bracket, and matching sleek design. Title: American Made Grills Estate 36-Inch Freestanding Grill - Natural Gas - ESTFS36-NG
Description: American Made Grills Estate 36 Freestanding Natural Gas Grill The Estate Grill series includes full-featured luxury gas grills built in the USA. Crafted with precision to meet your highest grilling standards, loaded with the features you expect from a grill in the Luxury class. 3 Red Brass Burners, Plus an Infrared Back Burner The Estate natural gas grill employs durable red brass burners, combined with ceramic briquette flame tamers to provide consistent heat (and, obviously, to reduce flare-ups). The 3 burners deliver 78,000 BTUs beneath a total grilling area of over 1,000 square inches. You don't often see red brass used in grill burners, primarily because it's more expensive than stainless steel. And, let's face it, it looks cooler! In addition, you'll enjoy the back infrared burner, which puts out 20,000 BTUs to roast meats on the (included) rotisserie. Stainless Steel Construction Constructed with 304 stainless steel including heavy-duty 9 mm cooking grates, 18-gauge double-lined hood with spring assist and a full-width hood handle. the AMG Estate grill is built to last and give you years of reliable service. Blue Knob Lighting You should never have to guess at what levels your burners are set, especially after dark. The American Made Grill Estate series includes blue illumination above each knob to help you see what you're doing no matter the time of day. Interior Halogen Lighting Speaking of grilling at night, is there anything worse than opening the hood and not really seeing what's going on in there? With the Estate series, when you open the hood halogen lights illuminate your cooking surface. Never squint again or be tempted to get a closer look at the meat (and get an accidental suntan on your face) to see if it's ready to flip, or how close it is to done. Stainless Steel Grill Cart with Ample Storage Talk about grilling convenience! The Estate 36 Natural Gas Grill Cart features magnetic access door with 2-drawer storage, 2 collapsible shelves, tank storage, an interior door condiment tray, ventilation, and locking caster wheels. It arrives fully assembled . Rotisserie Spit Storage Keep your rotisserie spit close by with integrated storage built into the grill. Rotisserie kit is included. Made in the USA? You bet! It's in the name: American Made Grills are built, tested, and serviced in the USA. American Made Grills 36 Estate FAQ Can I convert the AMG Estate 36-in natural gas grill to propane? There isn't a gas conversion kit available for AMG grills, but they make a propane version with the same price, specs, and features, the ESTF36-LP . Title: American Made Grills Muscle 36-Inch Freestanding Hybrid Grill - Propane - MUSFS36-LP
Description: American Made Grills Muscle 36" Hybrid Freestanding Propane Grill No other BBQ gives you multi-fuel flexibility in such a high-powered grill. The 36" Encore Hybrid grill delivers a whopping 110,000 BTUs of grilling power with over 1,000 square inches of cooking surface and leaves nothing to chance, with solid stainless steel construction and a load of included accessories. Hybrid Multi-Fuel Capability Why limit yourself to a single fuel type? With the AMG Encore Hybrid, you have your choice of propane, charcoal briquettes, lump charcoal, wood chunks, or hardwood pellets! With its creative Multi-Fuel Tray System, grilling with any combination of solid fuels places innovation in the hands of the BBQ chef. Note: While you can cook with pellets, the grill doesn't include a hopper/auger mechanism. Super-cool Design Reminiscent of a 1969 Shelby Mustang GT 350 You will be hard-pressed to find another grill designed to look like a classic muscle car. In fact, save your time. There aren't any (though this grill is also available in a 54" version!). It's the kind of unique styling that makes people stop and stare and wonder where they've seen it before. And best of all, when you run it wide open this baby smells much more appetizing than any car possibly could. Stainless Steel Construction Constructed with 304 stainless steel including the 14-gauge burners , 12-gauge burner covers , reversible 9-gauge V-shaped cooking grates , and 16-gauge double-lined hood with spring assist , the AMG Encore Hybrid grill is built to last and give you years of reliable service. Blue Knob Lighting Is there anything more annoying than having to guess at what levels your burners are set? The American Made Grill Encore series includes blue illumination above each knob to help you see what you're doing after dark. Interior Halogen Lighting Open the hood, and halogen lights illuminate your cooking surface to make it easy to check the progress of your food after the sun goes down. Never squint again or be tempted to get a closer look at the meat (and get an accidental "suntan" on your face) to see if it's ready to flip, or how close it is to done. Stainless Steel Grill Cart with Ample Storage Talk about grilling convenience! The Encore 36" Hybrid Propane Grill Cart features soft-close drawers, including a large drawer to store charcoal and wood, a propane tank storage drawer, a folding shelf with a cutting board, a towel holder, locking and non-locking caster wheels, and it arrives fully assembled . Rotisserie Spit Storage Keep your rotisserie spit close by with integrated storage built into the grill. Rotisserie kit is included . Made in the USA? You bet! It's in the name: American Made Grills are built, tested, and serviced in the USA . Included Accessories - a $1,200+ Value! Title: American Made Grills Muscle 54-Inch Freestanding Hybrid Grill - Propane - MUSFS54-LP
Description: American Made Grills Muscle 54" Hybrid Freestanding Propane Grill No other BBQ gives you multi-fuel flexibility in such a high-powered grill. The 54" Encore Hybrid grill delivers a whopping 176,000 BTUs of grilling power with over 1,600 square inches of cooking surface and leaves nothing to chance, with solid stainless steel construction and a load of included accessories. Hybrid Multi-Fuel Capability Why limit yourself to a single fuel type? With the AMG Encore Hybrid, you have your choice of propane, charcoal briquettes, lump charcoal, wood chunks, or hardwood pellets! With its creative Multi-Fuel Tray System, grilling with any combination of solid fuels places innovation in the hands of the BBQ chef. Note: While you can cook with pellets, the grill doesn't include a hopper/auger mechanism. Super-cool Design Reminiscent of a 1969 Shelby Mustang GT 350 You will be hard-pressed to find another grill designed to look like a classic muscle car. In fact, save your time. There aren't any (though this grill is also available in a 36" version!). It's the kind of unique styling that makes people stop and stare and wonder where they've seen it before. And best of all, when you run it wide open this baby smells much more appetizing than any car possibly could. Stainless Steel Construction Constructed with 304 stainless steel including the 14-gauge burners , 12-gauge burner covers , reversible 9-gauge V-shaped cooking grates , and 16-gauge double-lined hood with spring assist , the AMG Encore Hybrid grill is built to last and give you years of reliable service. Blue Knob Lighting Is there anything more annoying than having to guess at what levels your burners are set? The American Made Grill Encore series includes blue illumination above each knob to help you see what you're doing after dark. Interior Halogen Lighting Open the hood, and halogen lights illuminate your cooking surface to make it easy to check the progress of your food after the sun goes down. Never squint again or be tempted to get a closer look at the meat (and get an accidental "suntan" on your face) to see if it's ready to flip, or how close it is to done. Stainless Steel Grill Cart with Ample Storage Talk about grilling convenience! The Encore 54" Hybrid Propane Grill Cart features soft-close drawers, including a large drawer to store charcoal and wood, a propane tank storage drawer, a folding shelf with a cutting board, a towel holder, locking and non-locking caster wheels, and it arrives fully assembled . Rotisserie Spit Storage Keep your rotisserie spit close by with integrated storage built into the grill. Rotisserie kit is included . Made in the USA? You bet! It's in the name: American Made Grills are built, tested, and serviced in the USA . Included Accessories - a $1,500+ Value! The 36" Encore Hybrid grill delivers a whopping 110,000 BTUs of grilling power with over 1,000 square inches of cooking surface and leaves nothing to chance, with solid stainless steel construction and a load of included accessories. Hybrid Multi-Fuel Capability Why limit yourself to a single fuel type? Never squint again or be tempted to get a closer look at the meat (and get an accidental "suntan" on your face) to see if it's ready to flip, or how close it is to done. Title: American Made Grills Muscle 54-Inch Hybrid Grill - Propane - MUS54-LP
Description: American Made Grills Muscle 54" Hybrid Built-in Propane Grill No other BBQ gives you multi-fuel flexibility in such a high-powered grill. The 54" Encore Hybrid grill delivers a whopping 176,000 BTUs of grilling power with over 1,600 square inches of cooking surface and leaves nothing to chance, with solid stainless steel construction and a load of included accessories. Hybrid Multi-Fuel Capability Why limit yourself to a single fuel type? With the AMG Encore Hybrid, you have your choice of propane, charcoal briquettes, lump charcoal, wood chunks, or hardwood pellets! With its creative Multi-Fuel Tray System, grilling with any combination of solid fuels places innovation in the hands of the BBQ chef. Note: While you can cook with pellets, the grill doesn't include a hopper/auger mechanism. Super-cool Design Reminiscent of a 1969 Shelby Mustang GT 350 You will be hard-pressed to find another grill designed to look like a classic muscle car. In fact, save your time. There aren't any (though this grill is also available in a 54" version!). It's the kind of unique styling that makes people stop and stare and wonder where they've seen it before. And best of all, when you run it wide open this baby smells much more appetizing than any car possibly could. Stainless Steel Construction Constructed with 304 stainless steel including the 14-gauge burners , 12-gauge burner covers , reversible 9-gauge V-shaped cooking grates , and 16-gauge double-lined hood with spring assist , the AMG Encore Hybrid grill is built to last and give you years of reliable service. Blue Knob Lighting Is there anything more annoying than having to guess at what levels your burners are set? The American Made Grill Encore series includes blue illumination above each knob to help you see what you're doing after dark. Interior Halogen Lighting Open the hood, and halogen lights illuminate your cooking surface to make it easy to check the progress of your food after the sun goes down. Never squint again or be tempted to get a closer look at the meat (and get an accidental "suntan" on your face) to see if it's ready to flip, or how close it is to done. Title: American Made Grills Estate 42-Inch Grill - Propane - EST42-LP
Description: American Made Grills Estate 42 Built-in Propane Grill The Estate Grill series includes full-featured luxury gas grills built in the USA. Crafted with precision to meet your highest grilling standards, loaded with the features you expect from a grill in the Luxury class. 3 Red Brass Burners, Plus an Infrared Back Burner The Estate propane grill employs durable red brass burners, combined with ceramic briquette flame tamers to provide consistent heat (and, obviously, to reduce flare-ups). The 3 burners deliver 78,000 BTUs beneath a total grilling area of over 1,000 square inches. You don't often see red brass used in grill burners, primarily because it's more expensive than stainless steel. And, let's face it, it looks cooler! In addition, you'll enjoy the back infrared burner, which puts out 20,000 BTUs to roast meats on the (included) rotisserie. Stainless Steel Construction Constructed with 304 stainless steel including heavy-duty 9 mm cooking grates, 18-gauge double-lined hood with spring assist, and a full-width hood handle. the AMG Estate grill is built to last and give you years of reliable service. Blue Knob Lighting You should never have to guess at what levels your burners are set, especially after dark. The American Made Grill Estate series includes blue illumination above each knob to help you see what you're doing no matter the time of day. Interior Halogen Lighting Speaking of grilling at night, is there anything worse than opening the hood and not really seeing what's going on in there? With the Estate series, when you open the hood halogen lights illuminate your cooking surface. Never squint again or be tempted to get a closer look at the meat (and get an accidental suntan on your face) to see if it's ready to flip, or how close it is to done. Rotisserie Spit Storage Keep your rotisserie spit close by with integrated storage built into the grill. Rotisserie kit is included. Made in the USA? You bet! It's in the name: American Made Grills are built, tested, and serviced in the USA. American Made Grills 42 Estate FAQ How big is the AMG 42 Estate grill? The Estate 42 Built-in grill is 49.83-in wide, 29.61-in deep, and 25.45-in high. What are the cutout dimensions for the American Made Grill 42 Estate? The Estate 42 grill requires a cutout 40.75-in wide, 21.625-in deep, and 10.25-in high. Can I convert the AMG Estate 42-in propane grill to natural gas? There isn't a gas conversion kit available for AMG grills, but they make a natural gas version with the same price, specs and features, the EST42-NG . Do I need to use an insulated grill jacket with the AMG 42 Estate built-in grill? If you are installing the grill into a combustible structure, or near combustible materials, we strongly recommend using an insulated grill liner, AMG model GL-EST42 . Blue Knob Lighting Is there anything more annoying than having to guess at what levels your burners are set? Title: American Made Grills Encore 36-Inch Hybrid Grill - Natural Gas - ENC36-NG
Description: American Made Grills Encore 36" Hybrid Built-in Natural Gas Grill No other grill gives you multi-fuel flexibility in such a high-powered BBQ. The 36" Encore Hybrid grill delivers a whopping 110,000 BTUs of grilling power and leaves nothing to chance, with solid stainless steel construction and a load of included accessories. Hybrid Multi-Fuel Capability Why limit yourself to a single fuel type? With the AMG Encore Hybrid, you have your choice of natural gas, charcoal briquettes, lump charcoal, wood chunks, or hardwood pellets! With its creative Multi-Fuel Tray System, grilling with any combination of solid fuels places innovation in the hands of the BBQ chef. Note: While you can cook with pellets, the grill doesn't include a hopper/auger mechanism. Stainless Steel Construction Constructed with 304 stainless steel including the 14-gauge burners , 12-gauge burner covers , reversible 9-gauge V-shaped cooking grates , and 16-gauge double-lined hood with spring assist , the AMG Encore Hybrid grill is built to last and give you years of reliable service. Blue Knob Lighting Is there anything more annoying than having to guess at what levels your burners are set? The American Made Grill Encore series includes blue illumination above each knob to help you see what you're doing after dark. Interior Halogen Lighting Open the hood, and halogen lights illuminate your cooking surface to make it easy to check the progress of your food after the sun goes down. Never squint again or be tempted to get a closer look at the meat (and get an accidental "suntan" on your face) to see if it's ready to flip, or how close it is to done. Rotisserie Spit Storage Keep your rotisserie spit close by with integrated storage built into the grill. Rotisserie kit is included . Made in the USA? You bet! It's in the name: American Made Grills are built, tested, and serviced in the USA . Included Accessories - a $1,200+ Value! Each American Made Grill Encore Hybrid grill comes with: Rotisserie Kit Heavy Duty PVC Grill Cover Grate Lifting Tool Stainless Steel Griddle Drop-in Infrared Sear Burner Leather Gloves Fuel Kit (wood & charcoal) Care Kit American Made Grills 36" Encore Hybrid FAQ How big is the AMG 36" Encore built-in grill? The Encore 36" Built-in grill is 37-in wide, 33.25-in deep, and 33-in high. What are the cutout dimensions for the American Made Grill 36" Encore? The Encore 36" grill requires a cutout 35-in wide, 25-in deep, and 15-in high. Do I need to use an insulated grill jacket with the AMG 36" Encore built-in grill? If you are installing the grill into a combustible structure, or near combustible materials, we strongly recommend using an insulated grill liner, AMG model GL-AMG36 . Title: American Made Grills Muscle 54-Inch Hybrid Grill 3-Piece Propane Gas Outdoor Kitchen Package - MUS54-LP-3PC-PROMO
Description: American Made Grills Muscle 54 Hybrid Built-in Propane Grill No other BBQ gives you multi-fuel flexibility in such a high-powered grill. The 54 Encore Hybrid grill delivers a whopping 176,000 BTUs of grilling power with over 1,600 square inches of cooking surface and leaves nothing to chance, with solid stainless steel construction and a load of included accessories. Hybrid Multi-Fuel Capability Why limit yourself to a single fuel type? With the AMG Encore Hybrid, you have your choice of propane, charcoal briquettes, lump charcoal, wood chunks, or hardwood pellets! With its creative Multi-Fuel Tray System, grilling with any combination of solid fuels places innovation in the hands of the BBQ chef. Note: While you can cook with pellets, the grill doesnt include a hopper/auger mechanism. Super-cool Design Reminiscent of a 1969 Shelby Mustang GT 350 You will be hard-pressed to find another grill designed to look like a classic muscle car. In fact, save your time. There arent any (though this grill is also available in a 54 version!). Its the kind of unique styling that makes people stop and stare and wonder where theyve seen it before. And best of all, when you run it wide open this baby smells much more appetizing than any car possibly could. Stainless Steel Construction Constructed with 304 stainless steel including the 14-gauge burners , 12-gauge burner covers , reversible 9-gauge V-shaped cooking grates , and 16-gauge double-lined hood with spring assist , the AMG Encore Hybrid grill is built to last and give you years of reliable service. Blue Knob Lighting Is there anything more annoying than having to guess at what levels your burners are set? The American Made Grill Encore series includes blue illumination above each knob to help you see what youre doing after dark. Interior Halogen Lighting Open the hood, and halogen lights illuminate your cooking surface to make it easy to check the progress of your food after the sun goes down. Never squint again or be tempted to get a closer look at the meat (and get an accidental suntan on your face) to see if its ready to flip, or how close it is to done. Rotisserie Spit Storage Keep your rotisserie spit close by with integrated storage built into the grill. Rotisserie kit is included . Made in the USA? You bet! Its in the name: American Made Grills are built, tested, and serviced in the USA . Included Accessories a $1,400+ Value! Each American Made Grill Encore Hybrid grill comes with: Rotisserie Kit Heavy Duty PVC Grill Cover Grate Lifting Tools Stainless Steel Griddle Drop-in Infrared Sear Burner Leather Gloves Fuel Kit (wood & charcoal) Care Kit The American Made Grills Power Burner is a beautiful addition to your built-in outdoor kitchen. Power Burners offer a larger surface area and higher BTUs, allowing for woks, shrimp or fish boils, and more. Add necessary and convenient storage to your outdoor kitchen with our 36 inch AMG Double Door. Offering easy access to your BBQ Island, storage solutions for cooking tools and utensils, and durable construction for the outdoors - our doors will make your outdoor kitchen efficient and functional. For a wonderfully sleek built-in look, all doors offer easy flush mounting and a handy magnetic latch to keep doors closed, secure, and orderly. Title: American Made Grills Estate 42-Inch Freestanding Grill- Natural Gas - ESTFS42-NG
Description: American Made Grills Estate 42" Freestanding Natural Gas Grill The Estate Grill series includes full-featured luxury gas grills built in the USA. Crafted with precision to meet your highest grilling standards, loaded with the features you expect from a grill in the Luxury class. 3 Red Brass Burners, Plus an Infrared Back Burner The Estate natural gas grill employs durable red brass burners, combined with ceramic briquette flame tamers to provide consistent heat (and, obviously, to reduce flare-ups). The 3 burners deliver 78,000 BTUs beneath a total grilling area over 1,000 square inches. You don't often see red brass used in grill burners, primarily because it's more expensive than stainless steel. And, let's face it, it looks cooler! In addition, you'll enjoy the back infrared burner, which puts out 20,000 BTUs to roast meats on the (included) rotisserie. Stainless Steel Construction Constructed with 304 stainless steel including heavy-duty 9 mm cooking grates, 18-gauge double-lined hood with spring assist and a full-width hood handle. the AMG Estate grill is built to last and give you years of reliable service. Blue Knob Lighting You should never have to guess at what levels your burners are set, especially after dark. The American Made Grill Estate series includes blue illumination above each knob to help you see what you're doing no matter the time of day. Interior Halogen Lighting Speaking of grilling at night, is there anything worse than opening the hood and not really seeing what's going on in there? With the Estate series, when you open the hood halogen lights illuminate your cooking surface. Never squint again or be tempted to get a closer look at the meat (and get an accidental "suntan" on your face) to see if it's ready to flip, or how close it is to done. Stainless Steel Grill Cart with Ample Storage Talk about grilling convenience! The Estate 42" Natural Gas Grill Cart features magnetic access door with 2-drawer storage, 2 collapsible shelves, tank storage, interior door condiment tray, ventilation, and locking caster wheels. It arrives fully assembled . Rotisserie Spit Storage Keep your rotisserie spit close by with integrated storage built into the grill. Rotisserie kit is included. Made in the USA? You bet! It's in the name: American Made Grills are built, tested, and serviced in the USA. Included Accessories - a $1,000+ Value! Each American Made Grill 42" Estate gas grill comes with: Rotisserie Kit Heavy Duty PVC Grill Cover Stainless Steel Griddle 26,000 BTU Drop-in Infrared Sear Burner Smoker Tray Care Kit American Made Grills 42" Estate FAQ Can I convert the AMG Estate 42-in natural gas grill to propane? There isn't a gas conversion kit available for AMG grills, but they make a propane version with the same price, specs and features, the ESTF42-LP . Description: This American Made Grills outdoor refrigerator is fully constructed in 304-grade stainless steel and features front venting allowing the refrigerator to be fully built into your outdoor kitchen. With 5.3 cubic feet of storage space and three adjustable wire shelves, your 24-inch refrigerator will be able to keep all your drinks and condiments cool. The digital temperature controls allow you to precisely adjust and monitor the internal temperature and include an audible alarm if the storage temperature rises above recommended settings. Title: American Made Grills Estate 42-Inch Freestanding Grill - Propane - ESTFS42-LP
Description: American Made Grills Estate 42" Freestanding Propane Grill The Estate Grill series includes full-featured luxury gas grills built in the USA. Crafted with precision to meet your highest grilling standards, loaded with the features you expect from a grill in the Luxury class. 3 Red Brass Burners, Plus an Infrared Back Burner The Estate propane grill employs durable red brass burners, combined with ceramic briquette flame tamers to provide consistent heat (and, obviously, to reduce flare-ups). The 3 burners deliver 78,000 BTUs beneath a total grilling area over 1,000 square inches. You don't often see red brass used in grill burners, primarily because it's more expensive than stainless steel. And, let's face it, it looks cooler! In addition, you'll enjoy the back infrared burner, which puts out 20,000 BTUs to roast meats on the (included) rotisserie. Stainless Steel Construction Constructed with 304 stainless steel including heavy-duty 9 mm cooking grates, 18-gauge double-lined hood with spring assist and a full-width hood handle. the AMG Estate grill is built to last and give you years of reliable service. Blue Knob Lighting You should never have to guess at what levels your burners are set, especially after dark. The American Made Grill Estate series includes blue illumination above each knob to help you see what you're doing no matter the time of day. Interior Halogen Lighting Speaking of grilling at night, is there anything worse than opening the hood and not really seeing what's going on in there? With the Estate series, when you open the hood halogen lights illuminate your cooking surface. Never squint again or be tempted to get a closer look at the meat (and get an accidental "suntan" on your face) to see if it's ready to flip, or how close it is to done. Stainless Steel Grill Cart with Ample Storage Talk about grilling convenience! The Estate 42" Propane Grill Cart features magnetic access door with 2-drawer storage, 2 collapsible shelves, propane tank storage, interior door condiment tray, ventilation, and locking caster wheels. It arrives fully assembled . Rotisserie Spit Storage Keep your rotisserie spit close by with integrated storage built into the grill. Rotisserie kit is included. Made in the USA? You bet! It's in the name: American Made Grills are built, tested, and serviced in the USA. Included Accessories - a $1,000+ Value! Each American Made Grill 42" Estate gas grill comes with: Rotisserie Kit Heavy Duty PVC Grill Cover Stainless Steel Griddle 26,000 BTU Drop-in Infrared Sear Burner Smoker Tray Care Kit American Made Grills 42" Estate FAQ Can I convert the AMG Estate 42-in propane grill to natural gas? There isn't a gas conversion kit available for AMG grills, but they make a natural gas version with the same price, specs and features, the ESTF42-NG . Title: American Made Grills Muscle 54-Inch Hybrid Grill 3-Piece Natural Gas Outdoor Kitchen Package - MUSC54-NG-3PC-PROMO
Description: American Made Grills Muscle 54 Hybrid Built-in Natural Gas Grill No other BBQ gives you multi-fuel flexibility in such a high-powered grill. The 54 Encore Hybrid grill delivers a whopping 176,000 BTUs of grilling power with over 1,600 square inches of cooking surface and leaves nothing to chance, with solid stainless steel construction and a load of included accessories. Hybrid Multi-Fuel Capability Why limit yourself to a single fuel type? With the AMG Encore Hybrid, you have your choice of natural gas, charcoal briquettes, lump charcoal, wood chunks, or hardwood pellets! With its creative Multi-Fuel Tray System, grilling with any combination of solid fuels places innovation in the hands of the BBQ chef. Note: While you can cook with pellets, the grill doesnt include a hopper/auger mechanism. Super-cool Design Reminiscent of a 1969 Shelby Mustang GT 350 You will be hard-pressed to find another grill designed to look like a classic muscle car. In fact, save your time. There arent any (though this grill is also available in a 54 version!). Its the kind of unique styling that makes people stop and stare and wonder where theyve seen it before. And best of all, when you run it wide open this baby smells much more appetizing than any car possibly could. Stainless Steel Construction Constructed with 304 stainless steel including the 14-gauge burners , 12-gauge burner covers , reversible 9-gauge V-shaped cooking grates , and 16-gauge double-lined hood with spring assist , the AMG Encore Hybrid grill is built to last and give you years of reliable service. Blue Knob Lighting Is there anything more annoying than having to guess at what levels your burners are set? The American Made Grill Encore series includes blue illumination above each knob to help you see what youre doing after dark. Interior Halogen Lighting Open the hood, and halogen lights illuminate your cooking surface to make it easy to check the progress of your food after the sun goes down. Never squint again or be tempted to get a closer look at the meat (and get an accidental suntan on your face) to see if its ready to flip, or how close it is to done. Rotisserie Spit Storage Keep your rotisserie spit close by with integrated storage built into the grill. Rotisserie kit is included . Made in the USA? You bet! Its in the name: American Made Grills are built, tested, and serviced in the USA . Included Accessories a $1,400+ Value! Each American Made Grill Encore Hybrid grill comes with: Rotisserie Kit Heavy Duty PVC Grill Cover Grate Lifting Tools Stainless Steel Griddle Drop-in Infrared Sear Burner Leather Gloves Fuel Kit (wood & charcoal) Care Kit The American Made Grills Power Burner is a beautiful addition to your built-in outdoor kitchen. Power Burners offer a larger surface area and higher BTUs, allowing for woks, shrimp or fish boils, and more. Add necessary and convenient storage to your outdoor kitchen with our 36 inch AMG Double Door. Offering easy access to your BBQ Island, storage solutions for cooking tools and utensils, and durable construction for the outdoors - our doors will make your outdoor kitchen efficient and functional. For a wonderfully sleek built-in look, all doors offer easy flush mounting and a handy magnetic latch to keep doors closed, secure, and orderly.
